---
title: Pork & Roasted Veggie Trottole with Parmesan & Parsley
description: In this dish, we've teamed the traditional Italian tomato sauce with seasoned pork mince and roasted veggies for a meal that
looks every bit as good as it tastes.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pork-roasted-veggie-farfalle-a2a6cd59.jpg
